race.comment: Competitive. ASAWIN (4) resumes and two back went close at Geelong in stronger than this. He's proven fresh and has jumped out well. Goes at this distance and can make a winning return. CHILLI REAPER (12) resumed beaten a whisker at Mildura heavily backed, and then raced favourite again at Wangaratta and had a slow recovery. Has had 36 days to get over that, and a bounce is likely. SUGAR AND SWEET (8) has been beaten a whisker at both starts this preparation. Has a wide gate to contend with, but gets in well with the 3kg claim and can be in the finish with average luck in the run. WICHITALL (2) is third-up and wasn't beaten far in a strong form race at Warrnambool last time. Comes back in grade briefly freshened, and has a low gate and the switch to Coffey. Has to be kept well onside.
